data.description: Located near the heart of charming downtown Arlington, this updated split level home boasts a peaceful yard that backs up to Portage Creek. Set up perfectly for multigenerational living or rental potential (no HOA), the upper and lower levels each feature two bedrooms, their own kitchen (w/new appliances), living rm, bathroom and laundry, with separate entrances for each level. On the upper level, enjoy a new covered composite deck with a view of the creek, and below it, a patio and fire pit area. Home has new roof, paint inside and out, gutters with leaf guards, newer water heater. Cozy up inside with the new gas fireplaces on each level. Home is pre-inspected and ready for its new owners! Come take a look and envision your new beginning!
